{"tid":1862682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人間公司癲到叫人番工，仲要繼續搞新年活動聚哂所有人？","createTime":"2020-02-04T18:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T10:24:56.000Z","uid":287401,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"fd959b92bec45d5729f8dfe9f553948f0c3790a2","tid":1862682,"uid":287401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T18:14:14.000Z","msg":"利申：借ac<br />\n<br />\n有間Real Estate Consultancy（四大行之一）不單止聽日開始取消Work from Home，仲要搞event聚集同事！<br />\n其餘三間行都唔係咁咖，唔知點解得呢間公司咁撚西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間間外資行，都起碼work from home到二月七號，<br />\n係呢間咁離奇，二月五號就叫人番工。<br />\n話就話如果有concern唔想番，會有flexibility比員工同番line manager去傾，意即拋個波比下面個浸高層/中層去決定，以家啲管理層真係易做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫人番工都算，仲要呢個禮拜連續兩日<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">繼續搞公司活動</span>，又舞龍又舞獅咁。<br />\n喂大佬唔好咁癲啦，大把公司close office兼取消團拜活動，頂你個肺叫人番黎，仲要聚哂一大班人係個豆潤咁細嘅地方，然後同大家講公司會保證大家嘅安全同衛生嘅工作環境？？？？？<br />\n出撚左事，你賠番條命比同事？？？？？<br />\n<br />\n仲要好多番左工既鬼佬都無撚戴罩......<br />\n我淨係想講，恭喜哂啊咁多位高層！公司既心意同事一定收到哂！<br />\n到時有同事咁不幸要入隔離病房或者隔離營，<br />\n公司啲鬼佬高層記住去探病！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e29af8bbdff287f5b4ec08829331b05563e8f2","tid":1862682,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T18:15:12.000Z","msg":"LIHKG 創辦人「連尼住」今日生日！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1862522\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1862522</a>"},{"pid":"ccfa3ffcdaf7233a69ed1d23d11fc9830e45491f","tid":1862682,"uid":